About Us
Merritt Square Mall is located in Merritt Island, Florida, proudly serving local area tourists and residents, including Kennedy Space Center and many high tech aerospace employees. Located near Cape Canaveral and Cocoa Beach, this enclosed mall is the one-stop shopping, dining and entertainment destination.
Offering anchor stores Dillard’s, JCPenney, Macy’s and Sears, as well as specialty retailers like Bath & Body Works, Finish Line, Victoria’s Secret and Yankee Candle, Merritt Square Mall has a store for everyone.
Plan to spend the day at Merritt Square Mall, attend one of our hosted community events, grab a bite to eat at one of our many dining options, and catch a newly released movie at the only theater in town, Cobb Theaters.
Merritt Square Mall has just what you need, For Every Occasion.
